type: software
title: "Governance-Driven Design (GDD): Formalizing Intent Before the Machine Runs"
version: 0.1.0
date-released: 2026-06-26
doi: 10.5281/zenodo.20938778
authors:
  - family-names: Shatny
    given-names: Michael
    affiliation: Semantic Intent
